Definition: usually together with a bond or preferred stock) that gives the holder the right to purchase a certain amount of common stock at a stated price
Example: as a sweetener they offered warrants along with the fixed-income securities
Synonyms: stock_warrant, stock-purchase_warrant, security, a, type, of, issued, by, corporation, usually, together, with, bond, or, preferred, stock, that, gives, the, holder, right, to, purchase, certain, amount, common, at, stated, price, as, sweetener, they, offered, warrants, along, fixed-income, securities
Category: noun.possession
